FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773076277
OL,3,CMurdered victim's family 'reliving'
OL,4,Cher death as they search for real
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FPeter Sullivan, now 68, spent 38 years
OL,8,Fin jail for her murder before his
OL,9,Fconviction was quashed and he was
OL,10,Ffreed from prison in 2025.
OL,12,FForensic advances revealed that DNA
OL,13,Ffound at the scene belonged to an
OL,14,Funknown man, not Mr Sullivan.
OL,16,FIn their first statement since the
OL,17,Fcase was reopened, and as part of a
OL,18,Fmajor Crimewatch Live appeal, Diane's
OL,19,Ffamily said they are "reliving that
OL,20,Fterrible time and all that it brings
OL,21,Fonce again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773076277
OL,3,CMurdered victim's family 'reliving'
OL,4,Cher death as they search for real
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"Diane was 21 years old with so much
OL,8,Fto live for. She had a beautiful heart
OL,9,Fand soul, and was full of love, fun
OL,10,Fand laughter which could brighten your
OL,11,Fday," her family said.
OL,13,F"The tragic loss of Diane has been
OL,14,Ffelt throughout our everyday lives
OL,15,Fwith a heartache that will never heal.
OL,16,FWe are now reliving that terrible time
OL,17,Fand all that it brings once again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773076277
OL,3,CMurdered victim's family 'reliving'
OL,4,Cher death as they search for real
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Rachel Wilson
OL,8,Fsaid, while DNA testing was in its
OL,9,Finfancy in 1986, police now have a
OL,10,Fclear profile that does not match the
OL,11,Fnational database, Diane's family, or
OL,12,Fher fiance at the time.
OL,14,F"Our work has continued for some time
OL,15,Fto locate Diane's killer and we will
OL,16,Fleave no stone unturned to find him,"
OL,17,FDet Supt Wilson said.
OL,26,@tD@Jrr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773076277
OL,3,CMurdered victim's family 'reliving'
OL,4,Cher death as they search for real
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"We hope that by seeing the original
OL,8,FCrimewatch reconstruction, it will jog
OL,9,Fsomeone's memory or encourage them to
OL,10,Fcome forward with information they
OL,11,Fhaven't previously spoken about."
OL,13,FPeter Sullivan has said he stands with
OL,14,Fthe Sindall family as they restart
OL,15,Ftheir search for justice.
OL,17,F"I really do feel sorry for them and
OL,18,Fwhat they're going through at the
OL,19,Fmoment, where they're back at square
OL,20,Fone," Mr Sullivan said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773076277
OL,3,CMurdered victim's family 'reliving'
OL,4,Cher death as they search for real
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,F"If they want my support when they go
OL,8,Fto court with the guy, when they find
OL,9,Fhim, I will be there by their side,
OL,10,F100%."
OL,12,FA #20,000 reward is being offered by
OL,13,Fthe independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,14,Ffor information that leads to an
OL,15,Farrest and conviction.
OL,17,FPolice are urging anyone, no matter
OL,18,Fhow small they think their information
OL,19,Fis, to step forward and help provide
OL,20,Fanswers Diane's family.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
